{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "More regulation for home-based childcare: nannies, maternity nurses & tutors",
        "additional_details": "We call on the UK Government to introduce more regulation for all home-based childcare professionals, including nannies, maternity nurses, and tutors.\r\n \r\nThis could include:\r\n \r\nA compulsory national register\r\nMandatory enhanced DBS checks\r\nMinimum training standards (including safe sleep and safeguarding)\r\nProtected job titles\r\nA clear system for reporting concerns and enforcing standards\r\nThis could improve safety, transparency, and accountability for families.",
        "background": "We believe that this sector needs more regulation. Anyone can call themselves a nanny, maternity nurse, or tutor without qualifications, training, or background checks. This can put children at risk.",
